annotations.description: I'm a giant Disney's Parks fan, today I'm talking about my favorite attraction, the Enchanted Tiki Room, and making a Dole Whip *****************************...
annotations.title: Need your Disney Fix? Make the Dole Whip at Home! Also rum! | How to Drink

16 oz. -or- 450 g. Frozen Pineapple

and an umbrella!
